 \text{Find the smallest possible integer } k \text{ such that } \\ 7^{348}+2^{5605} +k \text{ which is divisible by } 8 \text{ given that } 
a \equiv b \text{ mod } n
n|(a-b)
7\equiv-1\mod8
2^3\equiv0\mod8
